For evaluating claims and reasoning:

```text
Main Claim
├── Supporting Evidence 1
│   ├── Sub-evidence 1a
│   └── Sub-evidence 1b
├── Supporting Evidence 2
├── Counter-evidence 1
│   └── Rebuttal to counter-evidence
